channel.title: Some of my Models
channel.description:
I'm fairly new to modeling, only been doing it for about 2 or 3 weeks. I just thought I'd showcase a few of my things here.
My Fender Stratocaster model. Took me about 2 and a half hours total. The extra colors took like a minute each, all I had to do was change the mats. YES, I know that I accidentally cut off the headstock in the picture, but I'm too lazy to fix it. [url=http://i389.photobucket.com/albums/oo337/GergHealey/StratmodelsBIG.jpg]Strat Models.[/url]
Here's a few of my "ModCapes." My friend asked me to make these for him, so I did. [url=http://i389.photobucket.com/albums/oo337/GergHealey/Modcapegold.jpg]Black/Gold Gold ModCape[/url] [url=http://i389.photobucket.com/albums/oo337/GergHealey/Modcapepic.jpg]Red/Blue/Yellow ModCape[/url]
I'll post more when I feel like it. :\
Oh, by the way, if you wanna use any of these in your server, It's fine by me. I don't care. Just PM me about it.
